<h1 id="什么是e" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#什么是e" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 什么是e</h1>
<p>前面我们说了，如果一个函数，满足</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\frac{df(x)}{dx}=f(x)
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.113em;vertical-align:-0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.427em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">df</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>，那么，这个函数f(x)就是e^x。虽然这么定义了e，但是e到底是什么呢？</p>
<p>首先，由泰勒公式，我们知道一个任意函数f(x)可以进行泰勒展开。</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><msup><mrow></mrow><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><msup><mrow></mrow><mrow><mo mathvariant="normal">′</mo><mo mathvariant="normal">′</mo></mrow></msup></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><msup><mrow></mrow><mrow><mo mathvariant="normal">′</mo><mo mathvariant="normal">′</mo><mo mathvariant="normal">′</mo></mrow></msup></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
